# Meeting Scheduler Backend

A backend service built using Node.js, Express, Sequelize, and MySQL that allows users to schedule meetings while preventing overlapping time slots.

---

## Tech Stack

- Node.js
- Express.js
- Sequelize ORM
- MySQL
- JavaScript

---

## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone Repository

git clone <repository_url>
cd meeting-scheduler-backend

---

### 2. Install Dependencies

npm install

---

### 3. Database Setup

Open MySQL and create database:

CREATE DATABASE meeting_db;

Update database credentials inside:

src/config/database.js

Example:

new Sequelize("meeting_db", "root", "your_password", {
  host: "localhost",
  dialect: "mysql",
});

---

### 4. Run Project

npm run dev

Server will run on:

http://localhost:3000

---

## Folder Structure

src/
